data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION.  Tucked away but within walking distance to Waverly Schools!  Welcome to this Classic Traditional 4-Bedroom,1 1/2-Bath Home. Greeted by a covered Porch, step through the front door into the formal Living Room, leading into the Formal Dining Room, great for Family Gatherings!! The Kitchen has an Eat-in Area and steps into the Family Room. Enjoy the Fireplace! There is access and a view to the Backyard and Deck area. Fenced-in yard with a 2-car attached Garage.
